author: Kelly Wynne
title: Some Twitter Users Really Think Putin Released Hundreds of Lions in Russian Streets to Make People Stay Home
description: This is just the latest bit of misinformation related to coronavirus that's making the rounds online.
content: Some people believe that Russian President Vladimir Putin has released hundreds of lions into the streets of Russia as a way to keep people in their homes and stop them from making the coronavirus outbreak even worse. A bogus tweet that features a doctored ph… [+3812 chars]
